red all people to go to church once a week. The consequence of not attending church was a fine of 12 pence, which was a considerable amount for a poor person.","jurisdictionLevel":2}],"lifeSummary":"When Thomas Grante was born in 1518, in West Allington, Lincolnshire, England, his father, Thomas Mark Graunte, was 21 and his mother, Alyce Grante, was 10. He married Sarah Robinson about 1539. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter. He died on 11 January 1567, in his hometown, at the age of 49."},"et":{"1518–11 Jan 1567":"1518–11. jaanuar 1567","1518–1567":"1518–1567","1520–1593":"1520–1593","1541–1617":"1541–1617","1497–1569":"1497–1569","1508–1579":"1508–1579","1593":"1593","11 Jan 1567":"11. jaanuar 1567","1558":"1558","1569":"1569","1579":"1579","1567":"1567","about 1539":"umbes 1539","1520":"1520","1541":"1541","1497":"1497","1508":"1508","1518":"1518","1617":"1617","1549":"1549","W. Allington, Lincolnshire, England":"West Allington, Lincolnshire, England","Biggleswade, Bedfordshire, England":"Biggleswade, Bedfordshire, England","West Allington, Lincolnshire, England":"West Allington, Lincolnshire, England"},"fi":{"1518–11 Jan 1567":"1518–11. tammikuuta 1567","1518–1567":"1518–1567","1520–1593":"1520–1593","1541–1617":"1541–1617","1497–1569":"1497–1569","1508–1579":"1508–1579","1593":"1593","11 Jan 1567":"11. tammikuuta 1567","1558":"1558","1569":"1569","1579":"1579","1567":"1567","about 1539":"noin 1539","1520":"1520","1541":"1541","1497":"1497","1508":"1508","1518":"1518","1617":"1617","1549":"1549","W. Allington, Lincolnshire, England":"West Allington, Lincolnshire, England","Biggleswade, Bedfordshire, England":"Biggleswade, Bedfordshire, England","West Allington, Lincolnshire, England":"West Allington, Lincolnshire, England"},"fr":{"1518–11 Jan 1567":"1518–11 janvier 1567","1518–1567":"1518–1567","1520–1593":"1520–1593","1541–1617":"1541–1617","1497–1569":"1497–1569","1508–1579":"1508–1579","1593":"1593","11 Jan 1567":"11 janvier 1567","1558":"1558","156